				Hosting is provided by <a href="https://www.digitalocean.com/">DigitalOcean</a> (Toronto), managed with cPanel, delivered and secured by <a href="https://cloudflare.com/">Cloudflare</a>,
				while using <a href="https://panelbear.com/">Panelbear</a>'s privacy-oriented monitoring tool.
			</p>
			{{ svg.digitalocean() }}
			{{ svg.cpanel() }}
			{{ svg.cloudflare() }}
			{{ svg.panelbear() }}

		</div>

	</div>
</footer>
